      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2021 luxury sport sedan in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and subjected to a rigorous maintenance schedule at authorized service centers. The exterior features a deep Obsidian Black metallic finish, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that ensures a mirror-like shine with zero paint chips or swirl marks. The interior is equally pristine, featuring hand-stitched Nappa leather that still retains its factory-fresh scent, with no signs of wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Every electronic feature and driver-assist system functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is flawless, offering a smooth yet potent driving experience that feels exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle with a documented history of adult ownership and no accidents. It comes complete with two sets of keys, all original manuals, and a full service log. For the buyer seeking a vehicle indistinguishable from new, this is the definitive choice.",
